      "content": "that makes sense as a general overview, but for my debate i need to be really specific with the logic. can you break down the actual economic and social theories they used? like, instead of just saying \"racial hierarchy,\" how would a defender at the time have argued that segregation actually benefited the economy or helped keep neighborhoods \"safe\" and \"stable\"? i need the most coherent versions of those arguments to really test my rebuttals.",
